-- Honda Seeks to Build Car Plant in Russia, Economy Ministry Says
-- B y   E k a t e r i n a   S h a t a l o v a
-- 2012-01-16T10:21:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-16/honda-seeks-to-build-car-plant-in-russia-economy-ministry-says.html
Honda Motor Co. is considering
construction of a car plant in  Russia , said Dmitry Levchenkov, a
department head at the Economy Ministry.  Honda and the Russian government are looking at
possibilities for offering import tax breaks on car parts for
the plant, Levchenkov told reporters today in Moscow.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ekaterina Shatalova in Moscow at 
